    "title": {
      "rendered": "New Mobile App Will Change the Way Donors Give and Nonprofits Fundraise"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Give-App-Facebook.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright  wp-image-16497\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Give App Facebook\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Give-App-Facebook-300x298.jpg?resize=300%2C298\" width=\"300\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Give-App-Facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C298&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Give-App-Facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Give-App-Facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Give-App-Facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Give-App-Facebook.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>At long last a mobile app has launched that allows Americans to easily donate to any U.S.-based nonprofit in just a few taps. By partnering with <a href=\"http://www.guidestar.org/\">Guidestar</a> and <a href=\"http://www1.networkforgood.org/\">Network for Good</a>, donors can now give to their favorite nonprofits and manage their giving portfolio in one simple, very smart mobile app called the <strong><a href=\"http://www.giveapp.org/\">Give App</a></strong>.</p>\n<p>Launched on July 13, donors search the GuideStar database inside the app for their favorite nonprofit, enter their credit card information which is then stored for all future donations, and then tap to give. It&#8217;s a simple idea whose timing is perfect. All nonprofits would be wise to <a href=\"http://www.giveapp.org/\">sign up to access their Give profile</a> as soon as possible and then integrate this app into their year-end fundraising campaigns by asking donors to &#8220;Favorite Their Nonprofit on Give.&#8221;</p>\n<p>Still in beta and barely into their launch, this app is in its first stages of development. My guess is that over time the app will include badges for giving levels, special calls-to-action from your favorite nonprofits, social fundraising, year-end donation receipts, and perhaps even gaming dynamics to earn points that can be redeemed for prizes or promotions. The possibilities are vast and exciting. <em>Here&#8217;s how the app works for donors:</em></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Download the app and register.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/register.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16501\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"register\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/register.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/register.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/register.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Search for one of your favorite nonprofits.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/mobile-fundraising-app.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16477\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"mobile fundraising app\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/mobile-fundraising-app.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/mobile-fundraising-app.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/mobile-fundraising-app.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Select nonprofit.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/wildlife-sos.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16478\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"wildlife sos\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/wildlife-sos.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/wildlife-sos.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/wildlife-sos.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Tap to give to the nonprofit.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/wildlife-sos-app-giving-yeah.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16479\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"wildlife sos app giving yeah\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/wildlife-sos-app-giving-yeah.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/wildlife-sos-app-giving-yeah.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/wildlife-sos-app-giving-yeah.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Select donation amount ($10 minimum).</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/give-app-amounts.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16484\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"give app amounts\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/give-app-amounts.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/give-app-amounts.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/give-app-amounts.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Enter credit card information. It is saved for<br />\nfuture donations.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/entercc.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16486\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"entercc\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/entercc.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/entercc.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/entercc.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Opt-in contact information.</h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/opt-in.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16488\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"opt in\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/opt-in.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/opt-in.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/opt-in.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. Tap to give and receive confirmation email.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/thank-you-email.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16489\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"thank you email\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/thank-you-email.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/thank-you-email.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/thank-you-email.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Search for and select another nonprofit.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/rainforest-alliance.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16490\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"rainforest alliance\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/rainforest-alliance.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/rainforest-alliance.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/rainforest-alliance.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. Select previously saved credit card ad tap to give.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ending.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16492\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"ending\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ending.jpg?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ending.jpg?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ending.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. Review donation portfolio.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/donation-portfolio.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16493\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"donation portfolio\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/donation-portfolio.png?resize=450%2C675\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/donation-portfolio.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/donation-portfolio.png?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
